title: Go! Real Food - 2013 Edition.pdf Gooner
description:
Go! Real Food - 2013 Edition 

54.2 MB | PDF | 132 Pages | English

Note: Previously only available in Afrikaans as Weg Kuierkos, you can now enjoy the same delicious outdoor recipes in English.

Real Food contains more than 150 easy-to-prepare dishes plus camping menus and packing lists specifically compiled for weekend breaks and short holidays. Discover the secrets of making snacks for the masses and cooking in the bundu when you're far from everything, and how to prepare hearty brunches and sweet treats for friends. Real Food even caters for the little people in your party: quick and easy braai ideas and one-pot dishes that the kids will love. Vegetarians needn't despair , there's also a special meat-free menu.
Picnic along the way - Thai chicken pies, Mediterranean potato salad, meatloaf, muesli bars, crunchy chicken salad, almond banana bread, your week at the seaside sorted and quick dishes to make in a potjie.
